overview: July 17th, 2011 :: Dragon Gate Pro Wrestling presents Kobe Pro-Wrestling Festival 2011 from Kobe Hall. Matches include:  01. Kenichiro Arai & Taku Iwasa vs Super Shisa & KAGETORA  02. Ryo Saito & Genki Horiguchi vs Susumu Yokosuka & Rich Swann  03. Yoshihiro Takayama & Don Fujii & “Hollywood” Stalker Ichikawa vs Naoki Tanizaki & Kzy & Tomahawk T.T  04. Open the Triangle Gate Championship Match YAMATO & Masato Yoshino & Gamma vs Naruki Doi & Yasushi Kanda & Cyber Kong  05. Special Match: Akira Tozawa vs Shingo Takagi  06. Open the Twin Gate Unified Tag Titles: Dragon Kid & PAC vs CIMA & Ricochet  07. Open the Dream Gate Championship Match Masaaki Mochizuki vs BxB Hulk
title: Dragon Gate Kobe Pro-Wrestling Festival 2011
